{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4c4c4caa54","title":"楼见南下支队时的讲话","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"713c46ed95","index":0,"year":1946,"month":9,"day":27,"articleId":"4c4c4caa54"}],"tags":[{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"id":"e23dcf99fa","name":"发言","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji22","name":"毛泽东全集第22卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives8/main/mao-quanji/maoquanji22.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji22":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"65d82096d5","type":"paragraph","text":"楼见南下支队时的讲话口","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4c4c4caa54"},{"id":"50bcba9b41","type":"paragraph","text":"（1946年9月27日）","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4c4c4caa54"},{"id":"1ea579c40d","type":"paragraph","text":"你们不怕困难，不怕性，勇敢顽强，深入敌人心脏，敢于和敌人作斗争，打破了国民党反动派十万大军的围勒，胜利返回延安，这是我党历史上第二次长征。你们虽然辆性了不少同志，但是光荣完成了党交给的任务，你们是党的宝贵财富，也可以说是从战争这所大学里毕业出来的优秀大学生。1946年6月26日，国民党向中原解放区大举进攻，三五九旅在中原军区指挥下突围，于9月27日回到延安。图为三五九旅指战员一路长途跟涉回到延安。","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4c4c4caa54"}],"page":{"id":"b2c9dbafb8","publicationId":"maoquanji22","articleId":"4c4c4caa54","start":188,"end":189}}}},"__N_SSG":true}